ActDepartment of Human Resources and Skills Development Act
PrecisAppointment of PAUL MIKE MIGUS, of Val des Monts, Quebec, to be full-time member of the Social Security Tribunal for a term of six months and designate PAUL MIKE MIGUS, as Chairperson of the Tribunal on a interim basis, until such time as a new Chairperson is appointed, effective October 9, 2012.
